### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### 2. Create a new Endpoint to Monitor
POST http://localhost:8000/endpoints
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Google Health Check",
  "url": "https://www.google.com",
  "method": "GET",
  "interval": 30,
  "timeout": 5
}

### 3. List all Monitored Endpoints
GET http://localhost:8000/endpoints

### 4. Get a Specific Endpoint (Replace ID with a real ID from the list above)
GET http://localhost:8000/endpoints/YOUR_ENDPOINT_ID_HERE

### 5. Update an Endpoint
PUT http://localhost:8000/endpoints/YOUR_ENDPOINT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "interval": 60,
  "is_active": false
}

### 6. Get Stats for an Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8000/stats/YOUR_ENDPOINT_ID_HERE

### 7. Get Logs for an Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8000/logs/YOUR_ENDPOINT_ID_HERE?limit=10

### 8. Delete an Endpoint
DELETE http://localhost:8000/endpoints/YOUR_ENDPOINT_ID_HERE
